data.text:
Plan your journey Concessionary Travel m.connect

Bus and Coach Services across Moray

Bus travel across Moray provides easy and convenient access for local residents and visitors to most areas of the county. Services available include Moray Council’s own m.connect demand responsive bus service and scheduled bus services operated by the Council plus links to Stagecoach Bluebird’s commercial network of bus services and the supported services of Deveron Coaches.

Journey planning information is also available on the Traveline Scotland website on https://www.travelinescotland.com/ which offers travel options using bus, rail and ferry. Traveline Scotland also offer an app which can be downloaded to any smartphone.
